{"tid":1984093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵DSE期間加密班次　料繁忙時段額外增30班車","createTime":"2020-04-22T08:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T09:49:05.000Z","uid":241764,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ade6b4c981269388bc1f12939a3db5e2990026","tid":1984093,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:39:59.000Z","msg":"港鐵今日（22日）表示， 周五（24日）起中學文憑試（DSE）舉行期間將加強清晨列車服務，以方便一眾考生前往試場應考，各重鐵線（機場快線及迪士尼線除外）將分別提早於6時15分至6時30分起逐步加密班次，並會視乎需要加派後備列車行走，預計每日早上繁忙時段最多可額外提供約30班列車服務。<br />\n<br />\n至於輕鐵及港鐵巴士方面，部分行經學校區的路線包括輕鐵507、610、614P、615P 及751線；以及港鐵巴士K51及K73線，亦會在考試日早上6時45分左右開始按實際客量需求加派車輛行走。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200422/s00001/1587542621175/%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5dse%e6%9c%9f%e9%96%93%e5%8a%a0%e5%af%86%e7%8f%ad%e6%ac%a1-%e6%96%99%e7%b9%81%e5%bf%99%e6%99%82%e6%ae%b5%e9%a1%8d%e5%a4%96%e5%a2%9e30%e7%8f%ad%e8%bb%8a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200422%2Fs00001%2F1587542621175%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5dse%25e6%259c%259f%25e9%2596%2593%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%25af%2586%25e7%258f%25ad%25e6%25ac%25a1-%25e6%2596%2599%25e7%25b9%2581%25e5%25bf%2599%25e6%2599%2582%25e6%25ae%25b5%25e9%25a1%258d%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%25a2%259e30%25e7%258f%25ad%25e8%25bb%258a&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=2ae036ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200422%2Fs00001%2F1587542621175%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5dse%25e6%259c%259f%25e9%2596%2593%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%25af%2586%25e7%258f%25ad%25e6%25ac%25a1-%25e6%2596%2599%25e7%25b9%2581%25e5%25bf%2599%25e6%2599%2582%25e6%25ae%25b5%25e9%25a1%258d%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%25a2%259e30%25e7%258f%25ad%25e8%25bb%258a&h=8e2283d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200422/s00001/1587542621175/%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5dse%e6%9c%9f%